data.description: ***This is a VA assumable loan*** It has been a difficult decision for the current homeowners to make but it is time to let someone else enjoy this lovely property surrounded by corn fields and wonderful neighbors. I know they will miss the amazing views you have from any room in the house or while sitting and relaxing on the front or back porch. You are surrounded by nature and feel like the only person for miles, such peace and quiet, nothing to hear except the rustling of the corn fields or the sweet sound of the farm animals. There is a bonus room over the garage that would make for a perfect office or guest room. The property is currently divided into one main pasture with 5 acres and 4 .75-acre pins and is fenced and cross fenced. There is a 40x30 shop with its own 200-amp service and there is water run out to the shop, there is also a barn and a chicken coop.
